#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-oidc-auth0-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:security-architecture.adoc[Quarkus Security] provides comprehensive OpenId Connect (OIDC) and OAuth2 support with its `quarkus-oidc` extension, supporting both xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc[Authorization code flow] and xref:security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc[Bearer token] authentication mechanisms."
msgstr "xref:security-architecture.adoc[O Quarkus Security] oferece suporte abrangente ao OpenId Connect (OIDC) e ao OAuth2 por meio de sua extensão `quarkus-oidc` , sendo compatível tanto com xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc[o fluxo de código de autorização] quanto com os mecanismos de autenticação xref:security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc[por token de portador] ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/security-oidc-auth0-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With Quarkus, you can easily configure OIDC providers such as link:https://www.keycloak.org/documentation[Keycloak], link:https://developer.okta.com/[Okta], link:https://auth0.com/docs/[Auth0], and other xref:security-openid-connect-providers.adoc[well-known social OIDC and OAuth2 providers]."
msgstr "Com o Quarkus, é possível configurar facilmente provedores OIDC, como link:https://www.keycloak.org/documentation[Keycloak] , link:https://developer.okta.com/[Okta] , link:https://auth0.com/docs/[Auth0] e outros xref:security-openid-connect-providers.adoc[provedores OIDC e OAuth2 de redes sociais bem conhecidos] ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
